data.Name: Julius
data.message:
Hi Julius,

I noticed you on Instagram, my name is Maxou, I’m from France.

With my team we’re building an app named Eyes for young people like you and me. Our team is in Toronto right now.

We try through Eyes to give you the best way to use social networks, and of course, some fun.

We’re launching our Beta version in Denmark and we’d love to have you as a tester 😎.

If you’re in, just come back to me in DM! The app is free by the way.

See you 🤜🤛

Maxou
